ces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係唔想走，即使啲人講到外國有幾咁好，<br />\n但始終唔及自己地方"},{"pid":"7042a189a9c7fa51b01ccc048d65bcf190d2a441","tid":177212,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我剩係識講廣東話 我走唔甩無得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捍衛香港核心價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港核心價值係層樓wo師兄"},{"pid":"e5b847d77f86851200938cbf046032f7ef66e35a","tid":177212,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:59:41.000Z","msg":"如果自己屋企比賤人入侵，唔戰鬥選擇逃走<br />\n去到第二個度再比人入侵一樣只係選擇逃走"},{"pid":"8d4d4a4690c7789fcae47c9231d216dfa39acb65","tid":177212,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果自己屋企比賤人入侵，唔戰鬥選擇逃走<br />\n去到第二個度再比人入侵一樣只係選擇逃走</blockquote><br />\n逃跑可恥但有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0e05566f265d5e091d44eb3d157f5bac18fe58","tid":177212,"uid":46337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:02:47.000Z","msg":"點解遇到問題係我地呢班做主嘅走<br />\n點解唔繼續努力捍衛自己嘅地方<br />\n只可以講，每一場嘅戰鬥都係漫長<br />\n唔好因爲少少嘅挫折就比人打沉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我係咪太樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"cb08350258566c4d14591b8e68b680fa6d82457d","tid":177212,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"樓主要先討論下個問題核心響邊度先!<br />\n777個選委係唔係香港人?<br />\n有冇人用槍指住佢投票?<br />\n建制派又係唔係香港人?<br />\n屋邨排蛇餅嘅又係唔係香港人?<br />\n林病隔日去市區，乜人走去同佢影相?<br />\n<br />\n以上班人無論人數，動員力全部都多過你，<br />\n情願見日日有人跳樓都無動於衷，<br />\n因為佢地嘅既得利益全部縛埋一齊，<br />\n有乜辦法解決?"},{"pid":"9421c04180a2c65eb72b36a924864405a0efdd29","tid":177212,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"努力搵錢中，搵到最後一水都無埋就走<br />\n經過呢幾年我確信香港人嘅香港必死無疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事到如今支那人支配香港一切已成定局，左膠好本土又好再問責都無意思，搵筆錢去外國過番人類生活算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8b7c403e26e2d113b5cf6155f605d1588194a1","tid":177212,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"走，一定係走<br />\n望住呢個地方既人，我完全唔覺得自己值得為呢個地方而努力"},{"pid":"4f1814d487a704c5395287f4afd8620ef3090960","tid":177212,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果自己屋企比賤人入侵，唔戰鬥選擇逃走<br />\n去到第二個度再比人入侵一樣只係選擇逃走</blockquote><br />\n而家係前門拒賊 有人後欄放火<br />\n我勸你諗下為幾舊水撐林鄭個班金毛mk <br />\n再諗下個班短視唔為後代著想既老友記<br />\n<br />\n曾經我都好傻咁話守護我城<br />\n最後。。。我下年就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e026bf3873b87db3d5f21f0b1c729a006adf08","tid":177212,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"走到先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860e619f5ee0a95f0cf5d8e127446c68354fa4f3","tid":177212,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我剩係識講廣東話 我走唔甩無得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捍衛香港核心價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港核心價值係層樓wo師兄</blockquote><br />\n我有樓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788a59ac1a4c8d5d08eec6a71bbeae5356b635a1","tid":177212,"uid":41382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"走出去好過留係到等死"},{"pid":"51ec200b363eb9ff18f28fcf06de9ef037909931","tid":177212,"uid"